author: CBS4News
title: Trump Protesters Cause Traffic Delays

organizations.name: trump protesters cause traffic delays denver

text:
DENVER (CBS4) – Hundreds of President Trump protesters took to the streets on Friday night just hours after the inauguration.
The protesters started with a small group at the state Capitol on Friday evening. Some carried signs. (credit: CBS)
The crowd began to grow in size and then was on the move making their way from Civic Center Park to Interstate 25 and Colfax Avenue. (credit: CBS)
